ph'><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></p>

<p class=3DMsoNormal><u>Select Data<o:p></o:p></u></p>

<p class=3DMsoNormal><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></p>

<p class=3DMsoNormal>Click on the =93Select Data=94 button and choose the f=
older
where all your data is stored. The app will now search that folder and list=
 the
data that it finds.<span style=3D'mso-spacerun:yes'>=A0=A0 </span></p>

<p class=3DMsoNormal><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></p>

<p class=3DMsoNormal align=3Dcenter style=3D'text-align:center'><span
style=3D'mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape id=3D"_x0000_i1036" =
type=3D"#_x0000_t75"
 style=3D'width:303pt;height:145pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square=
'>
 <v:imagedata src=3D"Help_files/image011.png" o:title=3D""/>
</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=3D404 height=3D193
src=3D"Help_files/image012.jpg" v:shapes=3D"_x0000_i1036"><![endif]></span>=
</p>

<p class=3DMsoNormal><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></p>

<p class=3DMsoNormal>Once you have selected the data you can click on =93Sh=
ow Data=94
and the chart will be drawn. Here we draw the chart for one day only.</p>

<p class=3DMsoNormal><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></p>

<p class=3DMsoNormal align=3Dcenter style=3D'text-align:center'><span
